      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Inline Policy Statements\nSelfAssociateElasticIp: Associate/DisassociateAddress\n  (scoped EIP; instance/ENI wildcard \u2014 unknown pre-launch)\nSelfDisableSourceDestCheck: ModifyInstanceAttribute\nSelfRepointRouteTables: CreateRoute + ReplaceRoute\n  (scoped exactly to private_route_table_ids)\nSelfLookup: DescribeRouteTables (*)\nSsmSessionManager: ssmmessages:* / ec2messages:*\n  / ssm:UpdateInstanceInformation (*)",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "rect_25",
      "originalText": "Inline Policy Statements\nSelfAssociateElasticIp: Associate/DisassociateAddress\n  (scoped EIP; instance/ENI wildcard \u2014 unknown pre-launch)\nSelfDisableSourceDestCheck: ModifyInstanceAttribute\nSelfRepointRouteTables: CreateRoute + ReplaceRoute\n  (scoped exactly to private_route_table_ids)\nSelfLookup: DescribeRouteTables (*)\nSsmSessionManager: ssmmessages:* / ec2messages:*\n  / ssm:UpdateInstanceInformation (*)",
      "lineHeight": 1.3,
      "baseline": 171
    },
